	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64531097"><p>We see these all the time. The scammers seem to be scraping LinkedIn. We have had several instances of a new employee starting and within a few weeks start to get SMS and/or e-mail messages from C-levels asking for GCs or whatever.</p><p>It's part of our onboarding process now to warn about these types of scams.</p></div>
