		<div id="comment_body_64531135"><p>You know what a gift card is right? It's like really inconvenient money you can only spend at one place.</p><p>If you offer me a gift card, I'll punch you in the face: if you want to give me money, give me money but don't restrict where I can spend it. But most importantly, nothing says "I didn't know what to get you so here's money but disguised as something thoughtful to look less crass" than a gift card.</p><p>Gift cards are a terrible idea that need to die.</p></div>
